OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FArtificial intelligence has helped
OL,8,Freveal how plants are shifting
OL,9,Fflowering times across the world due
OL,10,Fto climate change, a new report has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FA global study using AI to analyse
OL,14,Feight million digitalised plant
OL,15,Fspecimens dating back a century
OL,16,Frevealed flowering has shifted by 2.5
OL,17,Fdays earlier or later per decade on
OL,18,Faverage, disrupting relationships
OL,19,Fbetween plants and pollinators.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FIt is just one of the ways in which
OL,8,Fconverting preserved specimens of
OL,9,Fplants and fungi that lie "hidden in
OL,10,Fcupboards and boxes" into digital
OL,11,Frecords is transforming the fight to
OL,12,Fsave life on Earth, experts at the
OL,13,FRoyal Botanic Gardens, Kew, have said.
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FNew tech is being applied to
OL,8,Fcollections of plants and fungi, from
OL,9,Fdigitising specimens to speed up the
OL,10,Fsearch for climate-resilient wild
OL,11,Frelatives of key food plants such as
OL,12,Fcoffee, to genome sequencing long-
OL,13,Fpreserved fungal species to find new
OL,14,Fmedicines or alternatives to meat, the
OL,15,Fexperts said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FThe approaches are highlighted in Kew
OL,8,Fscience team's latest "state of the
OL,9,Fworld's plants and fungi" report,
OL,10,Fmarking the 10th anniversary since the
OL,11,Ffirst such report, and drawing on work
OL,12,Fby 400 scientists in 40 countries.
OL,14,FThe report warns the threats to plant
OL,15,Fand fungi species are significantly
OL,16,Funderestimated, with less than a fifth
OL,17,Fof plants and only a tiny fraction `
OL,18,Fjust 0.6% ` of fungi assessed for
OL,19,Ftheir extinction risk.
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FAnd an estimated 100,000 plants and
OL,8,Ftwo million fungi species are still to
OL,9,Fbe discovered, with 4,600 new species
OL,10,Fof plant and 7,800 new fungi described
OL,11,Fby scientists for the first time in
OL,12,F2024 and 2025.
OL,14,FKew's executive director of science
OL,15,FAlexandre Antonelli said the new
OL,16,Fdiscoveries were "just scratching the
OL,17,Fsurface" and many of the newly
OL,18,Fdescribed species are threatened with
OL,19,Fextinction "from day one".
OL,26,@xD@ROUyD@HO]{D@LOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FBut Kew's sixth state of the world's
OL,8,Fplants and fungi report has a hopeful
OL,9,Fmessage, focusing on the power of AI,
OL,10,Fdigitisation and other technology to
OL,11,Fboost knowledge, information sharing
OL,12,Fand conservation efforts around the
OL,13,Fworld ` and its potential to do more
OL,14,Fwith coordinated international action.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FIt comes as Kew completes its project
OL,8,Fto digitise of its herbarium and
OL,9,Ffungarium, using high resolution
OL,10,Fphotography to turn 7.4 million
OL,11,Fspecimens of pressed plant leaves,
OL,12,Fflowers, seedheads, mushrooms and
OL,13,Fspores dating back centuries into
OL,14,Fdigital records that can be freely
OL,15,Faccessed and searched online.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FThe scheme, funded by the Environment
OL,8,FDepartment (Defra), opened every
OL,9,Fcupboard and box in the herbarium to
OL,10,Fscan the specimen sheets at 40 imaging
OL,11,Fstations, digitally recording up to
OL,12,F20,000 images a day, while bigger
OL,13,Fspecies such as palms had to removed
OL,14,Ffrom their boxes and carefully
OL,15,Frecorded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FKew's four-year project has thrown up
OL,8,Finsights of the past in its
OL,9,Fcollections, from specimens collected
OL,10,Fand logged by famed naturalist Charles
OL,11,FDarwin to the 6,700 specimens gathered
OL,12,Fby First World War service personnel.
OL,14,FThe digital specimens now form part of
OL,15,Fa network of 145 million records from
OL,16,Finstitutions and organisations
OL,17,Fworldwide that is allowing researchers
OL,18,Facross the world to access important
OL,19,Fcollections that once they would have
OL,20,Fhad to travel thousands of miles to
OL,21,Fsee.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FProfessor Antonelli said: "We can use
OL,8,Fdigital assets, artificial
OL,9,Fintelligence and other technologies to
OL,10,Freally harness the information locked
OL,11,Fin many of these specimens that have
OL,12,Fbeen here for centuries, and use that
OL,13,Fto advance science and conservation at
OL,14,Fa global level.
OL,16,FAnd he said: "We can use this
OL,17,Fdigitised information to discover new
OL,18,Fspecies, and also to reveal species
OL,19,Fthat have gone extinct or are likely
OL,20,Fto have done so.
OL,26,@oD@[OUxD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,F"We can track change in relation to
OL,8,Fclimate change and we can also unlock
OL,9,Fthe information in those collections
OL,10,Fin a way that is much more equitable
OL,11,Fand accessible to anyone, anywhere for
OL,12,Ffree," he said.
OL,14,FIn Costa Rica, researchers increased
OL,15,Fthe country's known fungal diversity
OL,16,Fby 20% by combining published records
OL,17,Fwith digital collections, while AI can
OL,18,Fbe trained to distinguish plants such
OL,19,Fas sedges and mosses to help
OL,20,Fscientists identify species more
OL,21,Fquickly.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FThe first global study of the impact
OL,8,Fof climate change on flowering times
OL,9,Ftrained an AI model to classify images
OL,10,Ffor the presence or absence of flowers
OL,11,Fand then applied it to eight million
OL,12,Fspecimens of 200,000 species.
OL,14,FIt revealed not only a 2.5 day average
OL,15,Fshift earlier or later per decade over
OL,16,Fthe course of a century but also
OL,17,Fvariations between regions, with
OL,18,Fgreater changes in the tropics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FDigitised records have also boosted
OL,8,Fwork on changes to flowering and
OL,9,Ffruiting of plants in the tropics and
OL,10,Fthe Arctic where fieldwork is
OL,11,Fdifficult, been used to map loss of
OL,12,Fspecies, safeguard protected areas and
OL,13,Fhelp with food security, the experts
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FProf Antonelli pointed to research
OL,17,Fpreviously carried out by Kew to track
OL,18,Fdown climate-resilient alternatives to
OL,19,Fthe current commercial coffee species.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FThat research was done using the
OL,8,Fspecimens in Kew's herbarium and took
OL,9,Fa long time, but with digitisation "we
OL,10,Fcould do it much faster with other
OL,11,Fspecies," he said.
OL,13,FScientists are also using digitised
OL,14,Fherbarium records, sighting histories
OL,15,Fand statistical models to estimate
OL,16,Fwhether species are extinct or simply
OL,17,Fundetected.
OL,26,@qD@dOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FAnd for the first time scientists are
OL,8,Funlocking the "dark matter of fungi",
OL,9,Fproducing high quality genomes from
OL,10,Fvery old fungal specimens in Kew's
OL,11,Ffungarium, including samples up to 180
OL,12,Fyears old.
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781581669
OL,3,CAI and digital tech used to chart
OL,4,Cclimate impact and extinction risk for
OL,5,Cplants
OL,7,FThe experts said the ability to unlock
OL,8,Fthe secrets of known species of fungi
OL,9,F` which make up less than 10% of the
OL,10,Festimated species out there ` could
OL,11,Flead to multiple new uses from high-
OL,12,Fprotein alternatives to meat to
OL,13,Fprotecting crops from pathogens and
OL,14,Ffinding plastic-digesting fungi to
OL,15,Ftackle pollution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
